# Admin Course Categories API Contracts

BASE_URL: `${API_BASE_URL}/v1/admin/categories`

## GET Many Course Categories

- `GET BASE_URL`
  - Get many course categories data
  - Each course category returned should have `txt:responseBody` shape
  - Note for backend:
    - Make sure to use laravel `paginate` to return the list of the `txt:responseBody`

```txt:requestQuery
{
  q?: string; // search query
  perPage?: string; // how many items per page
  page?: string;  // current page
}
```

```txt:responseBody
{
  id: string;
  title: string;
  slug: string;
  description: string;
  courses_count: number;
  created_at: string;
  updated_at: string;
}
```

